# Vivid UI Component Reference

This project is a standalone prototyping environment using the Vivid Money SME design system (vivid-ui). Components are pulled from the real `sme-web` GitLab repo and live at `src/shared/ui/vivid-ui/`.

## Key Architecture

- **Styled-components** with `DefaultThemeProvider` wrapping the app
- **1px root font-size**: `html { font-size: 1px }` — all `rem` values map 1:1 to pixels
- **Theme tokens**: Access via `useTheme()` → `theme.token.color.c6`, `theme.token.sizeUnits(16)`, etc.
- **Polymorphic components**: Use `component` prop to change rendered element
- **Transient props**: Styled-component props prefixed with `$` via `PrefixType<T>`

