## Theme Colors (light)

- `c1` — background (white)
- `c2` — secondary text (gray)
- `c3` — disabled text
- `c4` — borders
- `c5` — hover background
- `c6` — primary brand (purple `#7B61FF`)
- `c7` — secondary brand
- `c8` — error/destructive (red)
- `c9` — warning (orange)
- `c10` — success (green)
- `c13` — info (blue)
- `c16` — accent (pink)

## Theme Spacing

```ts
const theme = useTheme();
theme.token.spacingXS   // 4
theme.token.spacingS    // 8
theme.token.spacingM    // 12
theme.token.spacingL    // 16
theme.token.spacingXL   // 24
theme.token.spacingXXL  // 32
theme.token.sizeUnits(n) // n * 4 (rem)
```

## Code Conventions (from sme-web)

- Do NOT use `FC` type for components
- Prefer `type` over `interface`
- All pages/components must be `'use client'` (styled-components requirement)
- Document helper functions and exported props with JSDoc
